text.data-paper-data: {"raw":"SCREEN SHARING\n\nFind the Mirror View option at the bottom right corner and turn it on. If it is on, the team members will constantly see the same position of the canvas. To put it this way, your screens will be synced. Since different devices usually have screens with different dimensions, a dashed line indicates the area that everyone sees."}
